            <lg xml:id="TK146">
<l>pakaipāva maccam paḻiyeṉa nāṉku</l>
<l>mikavāvā milliṟappāṉ kaṇ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Hatred, sin, fear, shame—all four will never leave</l>
<l>the trespasser in another's "house."</l>
